<br>
During a break in the action, I kept casting Eye of Zomm in the wall so I could see if Nagafen was still up. (I got a shot of him the night before and wanted a better one.)<br>
<br>
I finally got a drop close to the lair itself and strafe-ran it to the dragon.  I have to admit I thought it was strange to see a few fully clothed corpses there.  Then I snapped the picture of Nagafen and clicked off the eye.<br>
<br>
Damn shame that he didn't go down.  Better luck next time. <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://webpages.charter.net/thewok/jarasig.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
